<F P=100> ISRAEL </F>
<H3> <TI>   Government Imposes Curfew, Closure of West Bank, Gaza </TI></H3>
<H4>   Curfew Throughout West Bank </H4>
<F P=102> TA2702104494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1000 GMT 27 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2702104494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The security forces have imposed a curfew on all 
Judaea and Samaria towns. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports 
that the curfew was clamped down on Nabulus, Qalqilyah, 
Ramallah, and Bethlehem, as well as their environs. The curfew 
on Hebron and its environs is continuing, and currently over 
600,000 Palestinians in the territories are under curfew . 
  Our correspondent Yo'av Aviv reports that security prisoners 
are currently rioting at the Megiddo prison in protest against 
the Hebron massacre. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

