<F P=100> LEBANON </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Big Explosion' in Church Reported 27 Feb; Casualties 
Reported </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2702080194 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon in Arabic 0747 
GMT 27 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2702080194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A horrendous crime with the proportions of a 
massacre was committed in the Church of Sayyidat al-Najat in 
Wata Zuq Mich'il a short while ago. A big explosion occurred in 
the church while worshipers were taking part in a mass. Initial 
information indicates that a large number of people were killed 
or injured. Casualties are being taken to the hospitals in the 
area, particularly the Sayyidat Lubnan Hospital, which is 
crowded with casualties. 
  The army and security forces have cordoned off the scene of 
the explosion and the church perimeter amid a state of panic 
gripping the area. Adjacent buildings were affected by the 
explosion along with citizens. We will give you further details 
as available. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

