<H3> <TI>   President, Others Comment on Church Bombing </TI></H3>
<H4>   Church Official Comments </H4>
<F P=102> NC2702153894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1250 GMT 27 Feb 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2702153894 </F>
