<H3> <TI>   Muslim Brotherhood Condemns Lebanon Church Bombing </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2802163294 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1515 GMT 28 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2802163294 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


