<F P=102>  TA0103072594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0700 GMT 1 Mar 
94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0103072594 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The release of 900 Palestinian prisoners will take 
place today. This is reported by our correspondent Moti Amir. 
In one hour, 400 hundred prisoners will be released from the 
al-Zahiriyah prison. The first batch from among the 500 
prisoners to be released from Qezi'ot today were released half 
an hour ago. Our correspondent reports that prisoners from 
Judaea and Samaria are being released from Qezi'ot this morning, 
while Gaza Strip prisoners will be released this afternoon. 
  Sufyan al-Zaydan, the Fatah spokesman in Gaza, says today's 
release of Palestinian prisoners will not bring the PLO back to 
the negotiating table because the number of those being released 
is insufficient. 

