Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Dr. Sa'ib 'Urayqat, head of the Palestinian 
delegation to the Washington talks, was injured during a 
confrontation between residents and the IDF [Israel Defense 
Forces] in Jericho at midday today. A shock grenade hurled to 
