<H3> <TI>   IDF Begins To Release Detained Palestinians </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0103193894 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1800 GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0103193894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1800 GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] today released 
570 Palestinian detainees from Qezi'ot and al-Zahiriyah prisons. 
By the end of the week 800 detainees will have been released. 
