<H3> <TI>   `Well-Informed' Sources Comment on Bombing Investigation </TI></H3>
<H4>   Prosecutor Comments on `Clues' </H4>
<F P=102> NC0203213694 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 2015 GMT 2 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0203213694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Higher Court Public Prosecutor Justice Munif 
'Uwaydat has met Patriarch Sfayr. Following the meeting, 
'Uwaydat said that investigation into the bombing at Sayyidat 
al-Najat Church has yielded some clues. He added: Such crimes 
are organized and well-planned. They are carried out in a 
manner that makes them hard to crack. 'Uwaydat disclosed that 
the investigating magistrate in the case will be named in the 
coming few days. 
  Answering a question, 'Uwaydat said that similar crimes, 
such 
as the al-Balamand bombing, were solved in the past. 

</TEXT>

