<H4>   Arrest Reports Denied </H4>
<F P=102> NC0103194294 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1915 GMT 1 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0103194294 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Security sources that are well-informed about the 
investigations into the explosion in the Sayyidat al-Najat 
Church in Zuq Mikha'il have denied reports by REUTER that four 
women have been detained and will be interrogated. The sources 
told our radio station that this report is totally untrue. 
REUTER had reported that the Lebanese security forces today 
arrested four women suspected of having taken part in the 
explosion in the church. The sources said the women were 
detained at dawn today and that initial investigations showed 
that they had planted a bomb next to the altar during the Sunday 
mass. 

</TEXT>

