<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The prime minister, Ms. Benazir Bhutto, has said 
that Pakistan will continue to assist the Afghan brothers 
despite some unpleasant events. Talking to representatives of 
nongovernmental organizations and international aid agencies at 
[name indistinct] Afghan refugee camp near Peshawar this 
afternoon, she said Pakistan wants the establishment of peace in 
