<H3> <TI>   'Urayqat: U.S. `More Israeli Than the Israelis' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0203141594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1100 GMT 2 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0203141594 </F>
