Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Sa'ib 'Urayqat has criticized the U.S., charging 
President Clinton with failing to take a firm stand against 
Jewish settlements and failure to back PLO demands for 
international protection. 'Urayqat called the U.S. response to 
the latest events inadequate. He charged the U.S. State 
